<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Outsider -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Outsider.label>外人</TravelCompanions.stages.Outsider.label>
  <!-- EN: I had no choice but to join them... i'd have died alone, but i'm scared what they might do to me. -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Outsider.description>唉，我别无选择，只能加入他们...我也许会就此孤苦死去，但我更害怕他们会对我做些不好的事！</TravelCompanions.stages.Outsider.description>
  <!-- EN: Third wheel -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Third_wheel.label>累赘</TravelCompanions.stages.Third_wheel.label>
  <!-- EN: I don't really know these people, should i stay? -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Third_wheel.description>我和这些人之间有种无形的距离感。或许我不应该继续留在这儿？</TravelCompanions.stages.Third_wheel.description>
  <!-- EN: Familiar companion -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Familiar_companion.label>熟识的同伴</TravelCompanions.stages.Familiar_companion.label>
  <!-- EN: Most jokes are on me and i get to do all the crappy work, but i seem to start being accepted! -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Familiar_companion.description>虽然他们仍在拿我开玩笑，我也干着所有的脏累活，但大家似乎也渐渐地接受我了！</TravelCompanions.stages.Familiar_companion.description>
  <!-- EN: Part of the gang -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Part_of_the_gang.label>团体中的一员</TravelCompanions.stages.Part_of_the_gang.label>
  <!-- EN: My companions start to value my skills and insight, i get to sit at the table! -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Part_of_the_gang.description>同伴们开始重视我的技能与观察力了，我终于可以和他们坐在同一张桌子旁了！</TravelCompanions.stages.Part_of_the_gang.description>
  <!-- EN: Trusted mate -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Trusted_mate.label>可靠的同伴</TravelCompanions.stages.Trusted_mate.label>
  <!-- EN: My companions are there when i need them and they can count on me! -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.Trusted_mate.description>我和同伴们相互信任，相互依靠！</TravelCompanions.stages.Trusted_mate.description>
  <!-- EN: True friend -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.True_friend.label>挚友</TravelCompanions.stages.True_friend.label>
  <!-- EN: We have been through alot together and always have each others backs. We would die for each other! -->
  <TravelCompanions.stages.True_friend.description>我们推心置腹，肝胆相照。我们愿意为彼此慷慨赴死！</TravelCompanions.stages.True_friend.description>
  
</LanguageData>